source: TEXT_CTSMYCMEDAL_00719_RESISTANCECOUNCILOR_000_000<tab>Good <var 08 E3E90C0D ((<var 08 E3E90C05 ((evening)) ((day to you)) /var>)) ((<var 08 E3E90C12 ((day to you)) ((evening)) /var>)) /var>, Blade <var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 03 /var>. How may I help you?
target: TEXT_CTSMYCMEDAL_00719_RESISTANCECOUNCILOR_000_000<tab>Was kann ich für dich tun? Geht es um Widerstandsorden?

source: TEXT_CTSMYCMEDAL_00719_RESISTANCECOUNCILOR_000_010<tab>Good <var 08 E3E90C0D ((<var 08 E3E90C05 ((evening)) ((day to you)) /var>)) ((<var 08 E3E90C12 ((day to you)) ((evening)) /var>)) /var>, Blade <var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 03 /var>. You have received all the accolades one might possibly earn from the Resistance, but if there is aught else I can do for you...
target: TEXT_CTSMYCMEDAL_00719_RESISTANCECOUNCILOR_000_010<tab>Was kann ich für dich tun? Du hast bereits alle Widerstandsorden, die ich zu verleihen habe, erhalten.

source: TEXT_CTSMYCMEDAL_00719_Q1_000_000<tab>What will you do?
target: TEXT_CTSMYCMEDAL_00719_Q1_000_000<tab>Was möchtest du tun?

source: TEXT_CTSMYCMEDAL_00719_A1_000_000<tab>Proof of mettle exchange.
target: TEXT_CTSMYCMEDAL_00719_A1_000_000<tab>Frontwissen-Marken erhalten

source: TEXT_CTSMYCMEDAL_00719_A1_000_001<tab>Resistance honors exchange.
target: TEXT_CTSMYCMEDAL_00719_A1_000_001<tab>Frontwissen-Marken gegen Widerstandsorden eintauschen

source: TEXT_CTSMYCMEDAL_00719_A1_000_002<tab>Inquire about Resistance honors.
target: TEXT_CTSMYCMEDAL_00719_A1_000_002<tab>Mehr über Widerstandsorden erfahren

source: TEXT_CTSMYCMEDAL_00719_A1_000_010<tab>Nothing.
target: TEXT_CTSMYCMEDAL_00719_A1_000_010<tab>Abbrechen

source: TEXT_CTSMYCMEDAL_00719_RESISTANCECOUNCILOR_000_100<tab>My apologies, Blade <var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 03 /var>, but you are no longer eligible to receive proofs of mettle.
target: TEXT_CTSMYCMEDAL_00719_RESISTANCECOUNCILOR_000_100<tab>Du hast viel geleistet, im Süden wie im Norden Bozjas. So viel wie kein anderer.

source: TEXT_CTSMYCMEDAL_00719_RESISTANCECOUNCILOR_000_101<tab>I am afraid there are only so many honors one soldier can receive.
target: TEXT_CTSMYCMEDAL_00719_RESISTANCECOUNCILOR_000_101<tab>Ich kann dir keine weiteren Frontwissen-Marken geben. Du hast bereits alles erreicht, was zu erreichen ist.

source: TEXT_CTSMYCMEDAL_00719_RESISTANCECOUNCILOR_000_110<tab>My apologies, Blade <var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 03 /var>, but you do not presently meet the requirements to receive proofs of mettle.
target: TEXT_CTSMYCMEDAL_00719_RESISTANCECOUNCILOR_000_110<tab>Es tut mir leid, aber du hast nicht genug Frontwissen, um dafür Marken zu erhalten. Begib dich wieder in den Kampf und sammle neues Wissen auf unseren Schlachtfeldern im Norden und im Süden.

source: TEXT_CTSMYCMEDAL_00719_SYSTEM_000_111<tab>At least <var 22 E802 ((,)) /var> mettle is required to receive proofs of mettle.
target: TEXT_CTSMYCMEDAL_00719_SYSTEM_000_111<tab>Um Frontwissen-Marken zu erhalten, musst du über mindestens <var 22 E802 ((.)) /var> Frontwissen verfügen.

source: TEXT_CTSMYCMEDAL_00719_RESISTANCECOUNCILOR_000_120<tab>You wish to receive proofs of mettle? Then let us have a look at your combat records.
target: TEXT_CTSMYCMEDAL_00719_RESISTANCECOUNCILOR_000_120<tab>Frontwissen-Marken? Dann lass mich mal sehen, wie viel du über unsere Fronten weißt.

source:
TEXT_CTSMYCMEDAL_00719_Q2_000_000<tab>You have currently amassed <var 22 E802 ((,)) /var> mettle.
Expend <var 22 E803 ((,)) /var> mettle to receive <var 20 E804 /var> proof<var 08 E2E80402 (()) ((s)) /var> of mettle?
target:
TEXT_CTSMYCMEDAL_00719_Q2_000_000<tab>Du verfügst über <var 22 E802 ((.)) /var> Frontwissen.
Möchtest du <var 22 E803 ((.)) /var> Frontwissen gegen <var 20 E804 /var> Frontwissen-<var 08 E4E80402 ((Marke)) ((Marken)) /var> eintauschen?

source: TEXT_CTSMYCMEDAL_00719_RESISTANCECOUNCILOR_000_130<tab>A reward well earned, I must say.
target: TEXT_CTSMYCMEDAL_00719_RESISTANCECOUNCILOR_000_130<tab>Und ob du etwas über die Lage an unseren Fronten weißt! Eine ganze Menge sogar. Hier, ich bestätige dir dein Wissen mit meinen Marken.

source: TEXT_CTSMYCMEDAL_00719_RESISTANCECOUNCILOR_000_135<tab>When you have made your decision, speak with me again that we might discuss which honors you wish to receive.
target: TEXT_CTSMYCMEDAL_00719_RESISTANCECOUNCILOR_000_135<tab>Wenn du genügend Frontwissen-Marken gesammelt hast, verleihe ich dir dafür Widerstandsorden. Du musst mich nur darauf ansprechen.

source: TEXT_CTSMYCMEDAL_00719_RESISTANCECOUNCILOR_000_140<tab>Though I have not witnessed it with my own eyes, I have heard tales of what one might accomplish with the blessings of these accolades. You would do well to earn more if greater glory on the battlefield is what you seek.
target: TEXT_CTSMYCMEDAL_00719_RESISTANCECOUNCILOR_000_140<tab>Sammle weiter fleißig Frontwissen-Marken, um dir noch mehr Widerstandsorden an deine Brust stecken zu können. Je mehr, desto besser, das ist klar!

source: TEXT_CTSMYCMEDAL_00719_RESISTANCECOUNCILOR_000_145<tab>There is not a soldier in all of the Resistance that has yet to hear of your accomplishments. Indeed, our historians are quite eager to chronicle the ventures of Blade <var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 03 /var>, war hero and liberator of Bozja.
target: TEXT_CTSMYCMEDAL_00719_RESISTANCECOUNCILOR_000_145<tab>Kein Kämpfer des Widerstands hat je so viele Orden an seiner Brust getragen! Deine Leistungen sind beispiellos. Du bist wirklich eine lebende Legende.

source: TEXT_CTSMYCMEDAL_00719_RESISTANCECOUNCILOR_000_210<tab>Excellent! Which honors do you wish to receive?
target: TEXT_CTSMYCMEDAL_00719_RESISTANCECOUNCILOR_000_210<tab>Du möchtest also, dass ich dir einen Widerstandsorden verleihe? Welcher soll es denn sein?

source:
TEXT_CTSMYCMEDAL_00719_Q3_000_000<tab>Which Resistance honors will you receive?
(Proof<var 08 E2E80202 (()) ((s)) /var> of Mettle: <var 20 E802 /var>)
target:
TEXT_CTSMYCMEDAL_00719_Q3_000_000<tab>Welchen Widerstandsorden möchtest du erhalten?
(Frontwissen-Marken: <var 20 E802 /var>)

source: TEXT_CTSMYCMEDAL_00719_A3_000_000<tab>Sun of Fortitude (<var 20 E802 /var>/<var 20 E803 /var>) | Required Proof<var 08 E2E80402 (()) ((s)) /var> of Mettle: <var 20 E804 /var>
target:
TEXT_CTSMYCMEDAL_00719_A3_000_000<tab>Eisenschild-Orden (<var 20 E802 /var>/<var 20 E803 /var>)
Erforderliche Frontwissen-Marken: <var 20 E804 /var>

source: TEXT_CTSMYCMEDAL_00719_A3_000_001<tab>Sun of Valor (<var 20 E802 /var>/<var 20 E803 /var>) | Required Proof<var 08 E2E80402 (()) ((s)) /var> of Mettle: <var 20 E804 /var>
target:
TEXT_CTSMYCMEDAL_00719_A3_000_001<tab>Blutrausch-Orden (<var 20 E802 /var>/<var 20 E803 /var>)
Erforderliche Frontwissen-Marken: <var 20 E804 /var>

source: TEXT_CTSMYCMEDAL_00719_A3_000_002<tab>Sun of Succor (<var 20 E802 /var>/<var 20 E803 /var>) | Required Proof<var 08 E2E80402 (()) ((s)) /var> of Mettle: <var 20 E804 /var>
target:
TEXT_CTSMYCMEDAL_00719_A3_000_002<tab>Lebensretter-Orden (<var 20 E802 /var>/<var 20 E803 /var>)
Erforderliche Frontwissen-Marken: <var 20 E804 /var>

source: TEXT_CTSMYCMEDAL_00719_A3_000_010<tab>Return
target: TEXT_CTSMYCMEDAL_00719_A3_000_010<tab>Abbrechen

source: TEXT_CTSMYCMEDAL_00719_RESISTANCECOUNCILOR_000_230<tab>My apologies, Blade <var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 03 /var>, but you require more proofs of mettle to receive such an honor.
target: TEXT_CTSMYCMEDAL_00719_RESISTANCECOUNCILOR_000_230<tab>Ach, sieht so aus, als hättest du nicht genug Frontwissen-Marken ...

source: TEXT_CTSMYCMEDAL_00719_RESISTANCECOUNCILOR_000_061<tab>If you have amassed sufficient mettle, we may speak again about any additional proofs you require.
target: TEXT_CTSMYCMEDAL_00719_RESISTANCECOUNCILOR_000_061<tab>Begib dich auf eins unserer Schlachtfelder im Norden oder Süden und sammle weiter Frontwissen. Wenn du genug hast, bezeuge ich dir das mit meinen Frontwissen-Marken.

source: TEXT_CTSMYCMEDAL_00719_Q4_000_000<tab>Receive a Sun of Fortitude in exchange for <var 20 E802 /var> proof<var 08 E2E80202 (()) ((s)) /var> of mettle?
target: TEXT_CTSMYCMEDAL_00719_Q4_000_000<tab>Möchtest du <var 20 E802 /var> Frontwissen-<var 08 E4E80202 ((Marke)) ((Marken)) /var> abgeben und dafür 1 Eisenschild-Orden erhalten?

source: TEXT_CTSMYCMEDAL_00719_Q4_000_001<tab>Receive a Sun of Valor in exchange for <var 20 E802 /var> proof<var 08 E2E80202 (()) ((s)) /var> of mettle?
target: TEXT_CTSMYCMEDAL_00719_Q4_000_001<tab>Möchtest du <var 20 E802 /var> Frontwissen-<var 08 E4E80202 ((Marke)) ((Marken)) /var> abgeben und dafür 1 Blutrausch-Orden erhalten?

source: TEXT_CTSMYCMEDAL_00719_Q4_000_002<tab>Receive a Sun of Succor in exchange for <var 20 E802 /var> proof<var 08 E2E80202 (()) ((s)) /var> of mettle?
target: TEXT_CTSMYCMEDAL_00719_Q4_000_002<tab>Möchtest du <var 20 E802 /var> Frontwissen-<var 08 E4E80202 ((Marke)) ((Marken)) /var> abgeben und dafür 1 Lebensretter-Orden erhalten?

source: TEXT_CTSMYCMEDAL_00719_RESISTANCECOUNCILOR_000_250<tab>Yes, this is the requisite number of proofs. On behalf of the Resistance, it is my honor and privilege to award you this Resistance honor.
target: TEXT_CTSMYCMEDAL_00719_RESISTANCECOUNCILOR_000_250<tab>Ah ja, das sieht sehr gut aus. Und nun verleihe ich dir deinen Widerstandsorden ...

source: TEXT_CTSMYCMEDAL_00719_RESISTANCECOUNCILOR_000_251<tab>May it offer you the courage and protection needed to overcome all who would oppose you, and serve to enhearten those who might fight at your side.
target: TEXT_CTSMYCMEDAL_00719_RESISTANCECOUNCILOR_000_251<tab>Dafür wird man dich auf dem Schlachtfeld beneiden. Und sicher wirst du die Herzen deiner Kameraden mit neuem Mut füllen!

source: TEXT_CTSMYCMEDAL_00719_RESISTANCECOUNCILOR_000_270<tab>If I am not mistaken, Blade <var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 03 /var>, you have now received all honors one might earn in service to the Resistance.
target: TEXT_CTSMYCMEDAL_00719_RESISTANCECOUNCILOR_000_270<tab>Oha! Damit hast du alle Widerstandsorden erhalten! Was sagt man dazu?

source: TEXT_CTSMYCMEDAL_00719_RESISTANCECOUNCILOR_000_271<tab>In all my time with the Resistance, no soldier has shown such dedication to our cause.
target: TEXT_CTSMYCMEDAL_00719_RESISTANCECOUNCILOR_000_271<tab>Niemand hat sich so um unseren Widerstand verdient gemacht wie du! Lass die Orden an deiner Brust prangen und erinnere uns daran, was mit Mut und Stärke erreicht werden kann.

source: TEXT_CTSMYCMEDAL_00719_RESISTANCECOUNCILOR_000_272<tab>We could never hope to repay all you have done for us, but know that, so long as Bozja stands, her people shall never forget the hero to whom they owe their freedom.
target: TEXT_CTSMYCMEDAL_00719_RESISTANCECOUNCILOR_000_272<tab>Du bist uns allen ein strahlendes Vorbild. Kämpfe weiter in unserer Mitte, damit wir an deiner Kraft teilhaben können.

source: TEXT_CTSMYCMEDAL_00719_SYSTEM_000_273<tab>You have been awarded full honors for your contributions to the Resistance!
target: TEXT_CTSMYCMEDAL_00719_SYSTEM_000_273<tab>Herzlichen Glückwunsch! Du hast alle Widerstandsorden erhalten und die höchstmöglichen Statuseffekte erreicht!

source: TEXT_CTSMYCMEDAL_00719_TALK_ACTOR<tab>
target: TEXT_CTSMYCMEDAL_00719_TALK_ACTOR<tab>（★未使用／削除予定★）

source: TEXT_CTSMYCMEDAL_00719_RESISTANCECOUNCILOR_000_200<tab>
target: TEXT_CTSMYCMEDAL_00719_RESISTANCECOUNCILOR_000_200<tab>（★未使用／削除予定★）
